  "inscription": "<br />  In honor of<br />   Ernesta Drinker Ballard<br />  1920-2005<br />  Ernesta was the moving force behind the restoration of the  Fairmount Water Works and these gardens.  Fairmount Park Commissioner from 1981 to 2002 and a founding  member of the Fairmount Park Conservancy, she was a civic leader,  a feminist, a beloved friend.  <br />  <i>\"The world is a better place if everyone is included\"</i> - EDB 2001<br />  Erected September 10, 2006",
